sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant Prog as Program
    participant SI as SanguoInference
    participant TM as TransformerModel
    participant V as CharVocabulary

    User->>Prog: dotnet run -- ask [SanguoModel]
    Prog->>SI: RunInteractive(modelDir)
    SI->>SI: LoadFromDirectory(modelDir)<br/>加载模型与 vocab.json
    SI-->>User: 提示输入问题

    loop 交互问答循环
        User->>SI: 输入中文问题 q
        SI->>V: EncodeText(q)
        V-->>SI: question_ids
        SI->>SI: 构造 encIds = [SOS] + ids + [EOS] + PAD
        SI->>TM: Forward(encBatch, decBatch(SOS+PAD), encValid, decValid(step=1))
        TM-->>SI: logits(step=0)

        loop 自回归解码
            SI->>SI: 从 logits[step] 取 argmax 得到 nextId
            alt nextId == EOS
                SI->>SI: 停止解码
            else
                SI->>SI: decIds[step+1] = nextId<br/>outputIds.Add(nextId)
                SI->>TM: Forward(encBatch, decBatch, encValid, decValid)
                TM-->>SI: logits(更新后的 step)
            end
        end

        SI->>V: DecodeIds(outputIds)
        V-->>SI: answer 文本
        SI-->>User: 输出“答: answer”
    end
